Subject: Re: [T2] at my wits end

You should have these wires:

On the positive side of the coil:
wire from the main wiring harness for 12v power
wire(s) to the electric choke and cut off selenoid
wire to reverse lights

On the negative side
wire to the coil

Hope this helps.

Brad Spear
